{
  "texts": [
    "• Furthermore, this research recommends a combination of both techniques (bibliometric analysis and topic modelling) for institutions, funding agencies, government, bibliometric database organisations to improve analysis of research performance.",
    "• In future research, we aim to explore other data sources such as Web of Science, Dimensions, OpenAlex to compare the publications about TM and see if the results are consistent across different databases.",
    "• To conclude, our findings call for increased collaborations so that multidisciplinary and interdisciplinary research approaches can be applied to TM studies to fully deploy algorithms optimally.",
    "Thus, this will enhance the usage of TM for literature review synthesis.",
    "Though this study's aim was achieved, it has some limitations."
  ]
}